In addition to providing sports facilities, the Recreation Centre is also involved in the Community which means the two nearby housing estates of Bierley and Holme Wood where the vast majority of the Tong pupils live. One example of the first aim is the Summer Playschool running during the school holidays from 22nd July to l6th August from Mondays to Fridays.
